```js
// ==UserScript==
// @name         Holodex Url Extract
// @version      0.1
// @description  Adds a button to get urls from all displayed streams. I have no clue how solid this is. Might work or break at any time. Pink love! Koyo Love!
// @author       Joshu
// @match        https://holodex.net/*
// @icon         https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?sz=64&domain=holodex.net
// @grant        none
// ==/UserScript==

(function() {
    'use strict';

    let extractButton = document.createElement('button');
    extractButton.style.backgroundImage = 'url("data:image/png;base64,")';
    extractButton.style.backgroundSize = 'contain';
    extractButton.style.padding = '0.5em 1em 0.5em 2.5em';
    extractButton.style.border = '1px outset';
    extractButton.style.borderRadius = '4px';
    extractButton.innerText = 'Extract';
    extractButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        console.log('extracting');
        let urls = Array.from(getVideoColumns())
            .map(o => o.firstChild.href)
        .filter(o => o);
        openModalWithText(urls.join('\n'));
    });
    document.getElementById('top-bar').children[0].appendChild(extractButton);

    function getVideoColumns(){
        return document.getElementsByClassName('video-col');
    }

    function closeModal(){
        Array.from(document.getElementsByClassName('streamlink-modal')).forEach(e => e.remove());
    }

    function openModalWithText(text){
        let modal = document.createElement('div');
        modal.style.display = 'flex';
        modal.style.flexDirection = 'column';
        modal.style.width = '50vw';
        modal.style.backgroundColor = '#fcfcfc';
        modal.style.padding = '1em';
        modal.style.zIndex = 1000;
        modal.style.position = 'absolute';
        modal.style.top = '10vh';
        modal.style.margin = 'auto';
        modal.style.left = modal.style.right = 0;
        modal.className = 'streamlink-modal';

        let textarea = document.createElement('textarea');
        textarea.style.width = '100%';
        textarea.style.height = '50vh';
        textarea.style.border = '1px inset black';
        textarea.textContent = text;
        modal.append(textarea);

        let btn = document.createElement('button');
        btn.style.padding = '0.2em 0.5em';
        btn.style.border = '1px outset black';
        btn.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
        btn.textContent = 'Close';
        modal.append(btn)
        document.body.append(modal);
    }
})();
```
